      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12">
          <section>
            <h3>Looking to join the Kosupure family and sell some stuff?</h3>
            <p>Here are Kosupure our aim was to simplify the cosplay buying and selling process, with so many fragmented sites it can be difficult to have a commonplace that removes all the excess clutter. Our other goal was to do this while maintaining cheaper fees than other platforms, at our launch Kosupure is taking NO CUTS OR LISTING FEES from your sales. That means, the only fees you incur will be through our payment processer Stripe which is one of the most secure and user friendly payment systems around.</p>
            <p>As a buyer you do not need to sign up as seller to make purchases, but if you ever want to list something you will need to.</p>
            <h3>Pricing</h3>
            <p>At Kosupure, <strong>we don't take any cuts or listing fees</strong>, but please be aware of the standard <a href="https://stripe.com/us/pricing">Stripe</a> pricing model.</p>
            <div class="row">
